description: This chicken stir-fry with noodles couldn't be easier. With just four steps and four ingredients, it's the perfect weeknight dinner recipe.
name: Simple Hoisin Chicken Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add chicken, noodles and remaining sauce to wok. Stir-fry for 3 minutes or until heated through. Divide among bowls and serve.
